									<h3 class="article-game-label"><div><a href="/battlefield-hardline" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Battlefield Hardline</a></div></h3>
										<h2><a href="/battlefield-hardline/ea-rewards-any-battlefield-hardline-player-who-owns-a-previous-battlefield-game">EA rewards any Battlefield Hardline player who owns a previous Battlefield game</a></h2>
