										<h2><a href="/magicka-2/magicka-2s-next-big-idea-is-artefacts-like-halos-unlockable-skulls">Magicka 2&#039;s next big idea is artefacts: like Halo&#039;s unlockable skulls</a></h2>
					<div class="article-meta">
						<time datetime="2015-02-18T17:40:55+00:00"><span class="field-content">18 February 2015</span><span>&nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;1 day 3 hours ago </span>&bull;</time>
